data.title: 2024 NHSCA High School Nationals Results, Brackets, And Schedule
data.meta_description: Follow results from the 2024 NHSCA High School Nationals along with links to brackets and a complete schedule.
data.text:
NHSCA High School Nationals go down in Virginia Beach April 5-7. Some of the top high school wrestlers in the country will battle to see who's the best in their grade. Follow the results right here as we'll be updating this article throughout the event.

Brackets are available on FloArena here.

NHSCA High School Nationals Schedule

*all times are Eastern Standard Time

Friday April 5th

8:00am- Boys Freshman, Boys Sophomore, and HS Girls Divisions (championship side to quarterfinals)

1:00pm- Boys Junior and Boys Senior Divisions (championship side to quarterfinals)

Saturday April 6th

8:00am- Boys Freshman, Boys Sophomore, and HS Girls Divisions CONSI Bracket Competition

12:00pm- Boys Junior and Boys Senior Divisions CONSI Bracket Competition

2:00pm- All High School Division Quarterfinals

4:00pm- All High School Division Semifinals

Sunday April 7th

8:00am- All High School Division 3rd, 5th, and 7th medal matches

8:00am- Middle School wrestling begins

10:00am- All High School Division Finals
